> Just one of many reasons why C++/CX is deprecated in favor of C++/WinRT.
Unfortunately C++/CX productivity features for XAML development were forgotten among those reasons, and C++/WinRT is far behind to catch up with C++ Builder versus what C++/CX was already capable of in 2012.